data.description: Nice one story home in Roanoke City near Downtown allowing to enjoy Market Square, Dr. Pepper Park, Greenway Walk, and other amenities. Double pane sliding door in kitchen installed 2020.  Front bedroom carpet replaced recently.  Also, hallway bathroom toilet and fixtures replaced.  Per the property history: the roof was replaced in 2013, new windows 2018, and water heater 2018.  Please come tour!
